h from "history" to "help"<br />\r\n *<br />\r\n * 1.0.0.0<br />\r\n * Initial release.</p>\r\n', 'Twitter PHP Skript', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'twitter-php-skript', '', '', '2008-05-04 23:37:10', '2008-05-04 21:37:10', '', 120, 'http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/?page_id=110', 0, 'page', '', 0); 
