INSERT INTO `v4_wp_posts` VALUES (223, 2, '2008-08-31 22:49:35', '2008-08-31 20:49:35', 'Attached you\'ll find three photos of the old and the new iPhone and their display brightness. Well, I found out these following points:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The old one (2G) has a more blueish light color while the new one (3G) seems to be more redish</li>\r\n	<li>The 3G iPhone is brighter at any compared level</li>\r\n	<li>The brightness of the 2G iPhone seems to change linear by moving the slider. The brightness of the 3G iPhone however seems to be exponentiell; almost linear in the first half but than almost no change in the second half. Well, looks like this is supposed to be a psychological trick somehow?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_224" align="alignnone" width="100" caption="iPhone display brightness comparison - 0%"]<a href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/iphone-brightness-comparison-a.jpg" rel="lightbox[brightness]"><img src="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/iphone-brightness-comparison-a-100x100.jpg" alt="iPhone display brightness comparison - 0%" title="iPhone display brightness comparison - 0%" width="100" height="100" class="size-thumbnail wp-image-224" /></a>[/caption][caption id="attachment_225" align="alignnone" width="100" caption="iPhone display brightness comparison - 50%"]<a href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/iphone-brightness-comparison-b.jpg" rel="lightbox[brightness]"><img src="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/iphone-brightness-comparison-b-100x100.jpg" alt="iPhone display brightness comparison - 50%" title="iPhone display brightness comparison - 50%" width="100" height="100" class="size-thumbnail wp-image-225" /></a>[/caption][caption id="attachment_226" align="alignnone" width="100" caption="iPhone display brightness comparison - 100%"]<a href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/iphone-brightness-comparison-c.jpg" rel="lightbox[brightness]"><img src="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/iphone-brightness-comparison-c-100x100.jpg" alt="iPhone display brightness comparison - 100%" title="iPhone display brightness comparison - 100%" width="100" height="100" class="size-thumbnail wp-image-226" /></a>[/caption]\r\n', 'iPhone 2G vs. iPhone 3G Brightness Comparison', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'iphone-2g-vs-iphone-3g-brightness-comparison', '', '', '2008-08-31 23:08:01', '2008-08-31 21:08:01', '', 0, 'http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/?p=223', 0, 'post', '', 0); 
