INSERT INTO `v4_wp_posts` VALUES (266, 2, '2008-09-12 20:28:20', '2008-09-12 18:28:20', '<a rel="lightbox" href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/09/itunes-genius.png"><img src="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/09/itunes-genius-100x100.png" alt="" title="iTunes Genius Logo" width="100" height="100" class="reflex itiltnone alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-250" /></a>The new service called <a href="http://www.apple.com/itunes/whatsnew/">Genius</a> for <a href="http://www.apple.com/itunes/overview/">iTunes 8</a> is just astonishing for me. This was presented in the "<a href="http://events.apple.com.edgesuite.net/0809dt4bs89/event/index.html">Let\'s Rock!" Product Show</a> on Thursday, 10th of September 2008. <!--more-->\r\n\r\nThis service stores all your media library information which it newly structures in a new iTunes database file called <code>iTunes Library Genius.itdb</code> ((Mine is about 147MBi by a 130GBi music library)) in your user\'s iTunes folder.\r\n(I\'ll write a bit more when I have time about what Genius is and makes it maybe a bit different to <a href="http://www.last.fm/">Last.fm</a>, <a href="http://www.spotify.com/">Spotify</a>, <a href="http://www.deezer.com/">Deezer</a>, etc.) with pros and cons.\r\n\r\nBelow you can see some screenshots of three songs I picked to test Genius against my media library. Hip-Hip (Dynamite Deluxe - Erster Song), Rock (Hard rain) and - of course - my lovely one: Oasis (Oasis - Live forever). And I think the result is very good (and will get even better, when more and more people are activating ((...)) their Genius?!) All playlist have lots of high rated songs in it, with almost the same genre. And not only new songs, but also every kind of year.\r\n\r\nA really good trick as I think is to add a <em>smart playlist</em> with the following criteria: "Playlist is Genius". That\'s all. Whenever you sync music with your iPhone from now on, the last generated Genius Playlist content will be synced to your iPhone oder iPod Touch. What\'s the advance of this than not just use Genius on the iPhone itself? Well, Creating a playlist out of a 8/16GBi collection is a quiet more random game than out of 130GBi ;-)\r\n\r\nBy the way: This is for Ricco who - I think - really will like this one: Also in iTunes 8 there is a <a href="http://www.apple.com/itunes/whatsnew/">new visualizer</a> called <a href="http://www.barbariangroup.com/topics/visualizer">Magnetosphere</a> Here a short <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=39_BWD5IJEs">video on YouTube</a>.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_244" align="alignnone" width="300" caption="iTunes Genius generated playlist by "Dynamite Deluxe - Erster Song""]<a rel="lightbox" href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/09/itunes-genius-dynamite-deluxe-erster-song.png"><img src="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/09/itunes-genius-dynamite-deluxe-erster-song-300x177.png" alt="iTunes Genius generated playlist by &quot;Dynamite Deluxe - Erster Song&quot;" title="iTunes Genius generated playlist by &quot;Dynamite Deluxe - Erster Song&quot;" width="300" height="177" class="size-medium wp-image-244" /></a>[/caption]\r\n[caption id="attachment_246" align="alignnone" width="300" caption="iTunes Genius generated playlist by "Shout out louds - Hard rain""]<a rel="lightbox" href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/09/itunes-genius-shout-out-louds-hard-rain.png"><img src="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/wp-content/uploads/2008/09/itunes-genius-shout-out-louds-hard-rain-300x177.png" alt="iTunes Genius generated playlist by &quot;Shout out louds - Hard rain&quot;" title="iTunes Genius generated playlist by &quot;Shout out louds - Hard rain&quot;" width="300" height="177" class="size-medium wp-image-246" /></a>[/caption][caption id="attachment_245" align="alignnone" width="300" caption="iTunes Genius generated playlist by "Oasis - Live forever""]<a rel="