INSERT INTO `v4_wp_posts` VALUES (393, 2, '2008-12-15 11:07:51', '2008-12-15 09:07:51', 'Briefly a little internal update status:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>I reset my iPhone to initial settings to see, if the slow performance is due to the jailbreak, the full flash disk or just an "other the timeline slowing" thing. I expect some changes after 2-3 weeks, which was the amount of days it took to slow down a completely fresh installation since <a href="http://www.apple.com/iphone/softwareupdate/">version 2.2</a> came out - We will see.</li>\r\n	<li>I\'ve updated my Wordpress blog to Wordpress <a href="http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/">version 2.7</a>. It was quick, nice and without problems. The admin interface is now really nice and I could cancel some plugins I used. During this change I also got rid of some plugins that slowed down my blog page speed and it\'s "running" quite fast now (<code>2.8</code> secs per page generating compared to <code>8.1</code> secs before). Why I did the update although I should now that the first bug-fix will come in t-7 days? Because I also wanted to bug-fix some issues: (1) The automatic plugin update did not work for my web hosting provider. Now it works again and updating security risky plugin versions works seamlessly. (2) The classic effect "It\'s definitely faster now!" came and I think: it\'s definitely a bit faster now. (3) When I wrote a post and previewed or published it, my browser always scroll down to the bottom of the page.</li>\r\n	<li>Since my <a href="http://cyberduck.ch/">Cyberduck</a> app is not starting anymore (is just freezes after the launch click) I temporarily switched to <a href="http://filezilla-project.org/">Filezilla</a>. Maybe someone had the same problem and can help me? Some post in internet forums state some solutions but they didn\'t help me or are not practicable (launch Cyberduck from DMG image...tss)</li>\r\n	<li>I removed some old websites from my ftp hosting (<a href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/wm06/">WM2006</a>, <a href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/wiba05/">WIBA\'05</a>, <a href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/v3/">Blog v3</a>, <a href="http://www.kreisquadratur.de/grubbedruck/">Grubbedruck</a>). If someone still needs files from it, please contact me via email, twitter, icq, skype.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Vorweihnachtsputz', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vorweihnachtsputz', '', '\nhttp://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/', '2008-12-15 11:50:57', '2008-12-15 09:50:57', '', 0, 'http://www.kreisquadratur.de/blog/?p=393', 0, 'post', '', 1); 
